{
  "id": "5bd6d728b5333c0014586b27",
  "title": "コントローラでもキーボードとマウスでも操作できるように",
  "created": 1530693318,
  "updated": 1531106569,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d1",
      "text": "コントローラでもキーボードとマウスでも操作できるように",
      "created": 1530693318,
      "updated": 1530714487,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d2",
      "text": "実験のたびにいちいちOculus上にインストールしてると時間がかかってしょうがないので、基本的な操作はコントローラのつながってないPC上でも試せるようにした",
      "created": 1531106328,
      "updated": 1531106372,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d3",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1531106328,
      "updated": 1531106328,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d4",
      "text": "キーボードでのカメラの回転",
      "created": 1530714508,
      "updated": 1530714528,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d5",
      "text": "code:cs",
      "created": 1530693319,
      "updated": 1530694495,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d6",
      "text": " void Update () {",
      "created": 1530694496,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d7",
      "text": "        if (Input.GetKey(KeyCode.UpArrow))",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d8",
      "text": "        {",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3d9",
      "text": "            camera.transform.Rotate(camera.transform.right, -1f);",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3da",
      "text": "        }",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3db",
      "text": "        if (Input.GetKey(KeyCode.DownArrow))",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3dc",
      "text": "        {",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3dd",
      "text": "            camera.transform.Rotate(camera.transform.right, 1f);",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3de",
      "text": "        }",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3df",
      "text": "        if (Input.GetKey(KeyCode.LeftArrow))",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e0",
      "text": "        {",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e1",
      "text": "            camera.transform.Rotate(camera.transform.up, -1f);",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e2",
      "text": "        }",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e3",
      "text": "        if (Input.GetKey(KeyCode.RightArrow))",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e4",
      "text": "        {",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e5",
      "text": "            camera.transform.Rotate(camera.transform.up, 1f);",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e6",
      "text": "        }",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e7",
      "text": "    }",
      "created": 1530694497,
      "updated": 1530695861,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e8",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1530714522,
      "updated": 1530714522,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3e9",
      "text": "マウスとコントローラーの両方でのレイキャスト",
      "created": 1530695842,
      "updated": 1530714548,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3ea",
      "text": "code:cs",
      "created": 1530695842,
      "updated": 1530695844,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3eb",
      "text": " if (Input.mousePresent)",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3ec",
      "text": " {",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3ed",
      "text": "     // PC Mode",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3ee",
      "text": "     ray = Camera.main.ScreenPointToRay(Input.mousePosition);",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3ef",
      "text": " }",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f0",
      "text": " else",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f1",
      "text": " {",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f2",
      "text": "     // Oculus Mode",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f3",
      "text": "     ray = new Ray(pointer.position, pointer.forward);",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f4",
      "text": " }",
      "created": 1530708172,
      "updated": 1530708178,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f5",
      "text": "pointer.positionやpointer.forwardを使っていたところはray.originとray.forwardにする。",
      "created": 1530695845,
      "updated": 1530714618,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f6",
      "text": "",
      "created": 1530714625,
      "updated": 1530714625,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f7",
      "text": "コントローラーのトリガーでもマウスの右クリックでも反応するようにする",
      "created": 1530695008,
      "updated": 1530714648,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f8",
      "text": "code:cs",
      "created": 1530694493,
      "updated": 1530695010,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3f9",
      "text": " if (OVRInput.GetDown(OVRInput.Button.PrimaryIndexTrigger) || Input.GetMouseButton(0))",
      "created": 1530695011,
      "updated": 1530695012,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3fa",
      "text": "いちいち上記のように書いて回るの面倒なので以下のようなstaticメソッドを作った",
      "created": 1530714649,
      "updated": 1531106557,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3fb",
      "text": "code:cs",
      "created": 1531106557,
      "updated": 1531106560,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3fc",
      "text": " public static bool Up()",
      "created": 1531106560,
      "updated": 1531106566,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3fd",
      "text": " {",
      "created": 1531106561,
      "updated": 1531106566,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3fe",
      "text": "     return OVRInput.GetUp(OVRInput.Button.PrimaryIndexTrigger) || Input.GetMouseButtonUp(0);",
      "created": 1531106561,
      "updated": 1531106566,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a3ff",
      "text": " }",
      "created": 1531106561,
      "updated": 1531106566,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a400",
      "text": "今後スワイプなどにも適宜キーボードを割り当てていく",
      "created": 1531106561,
      "updated": 1531106568,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a401",
      "text": "本格的にやるならキーコンフィグの設定画面を作るべきか。",
      "created": 1530714669,
      "updated": 1530714686,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a402",
      "text": "Page Up/Down",
      "created": 1530714652,
      "updated": 1530856998,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a403",
      "text": "Shift+Page Up/Down",
      "created": 1530856998,
      "updated": 1530857005,
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e"
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd6d728aff09e000076a404",
